{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341700/extras/steam-description.png?t=1725468380\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341700/extras/voice.png?t=1725468380\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341700/extras/2.gif?t=1725468380\" /><br><br>Cast spells by chanting, and striking heroic poses for enhanced magic effects. Learn and perform different spells according to the needs of the battle. Movement, strategic thinking and resource management are crucial in every duel! Be sure that you use every tool in your arsenal.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341700/extras/ai.png?t=1725468380\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341700/extras/5.gif?t=1725468380\" /><br><br>Engage in voice-based communication with 3D AI characters! During the tutorial stages, you will not only be able to learn everything about the game but also 'chit-chat' with the character that is guiding you with AI-generated conversations. Be sure that you don't get captivated by Lukia and actually finish the tutorial!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341700/extras/highligts.png?t=1725468380\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341700/extras/3.gif?t=1725468380\" /><br><br>Supports up to four players in multiplayer mode with 1v1 or 2v2 team battles and battle royales. Grab your partner or join solo with our matchmaking feature and get to play with other Wizards from all around the world.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2341700/extras/4.gif?t=1725468380\"